title: STAT+: Sanofi is reprimanded by a U.K. trade group for misleading claims about a Pfizer vaccine
description: Sanofi was criticized by a U.K. trade group, which accused it of making misleading claims about its RSV vaccine and disparaging a rival product from Pfizer.
